      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! I\u2019ve totally babied this car, keeping it spotless and always tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new and has been loved every mile of the way, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look\u2014I promise you\u2019re gonna fall in love with it! \u2728",
