    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of the 996.2 evolution, presented in collector-grade condition. It features the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, utilizing VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle and a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system. The chassis benefits from the wide-body Turbo-spec architecture, including the 330mm cross-drilled rotors and four-piston monobloc calipers. This example boasts a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a meticulously maintained cooling system with low-temperature thermostats. The factory-original paint retains its deep luster with zero evidence of oxidation, while the cabin's leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A mechanically flawless specimen for the discerning purist.",
