      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior finish retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing, the original factory floor mats are pristine, and every electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, documented service history from authorized specialists, ensuring it drives with the same tightness and responsiveness as the day it left the assembly line. No modifications, no accidents, and no excuses\u2014this is a turn-key opportunity to own a pure, collector-grade machine for the most discerning enthusiast.",
